The paper deals with the problem of computing the largest bond and largest $st$-bond of a graph, which are related to graph connectivity. This makes it likely to belong to the Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Computational Geometry (cs.CG), Computational Complexity (cs.CC), and Graph Theory (cs.GT) sub-categories.
